511
00:24:19.210 --> 00:24:21.410
All right. well. let's get
him prepped for a CAT scan.

512
00:24:21.411 --> 00:24:22.812
SÃ­. Captain.

513
00:24:22.881 --> 00:24:24.680
Oh. and you.

514
00:24:24.749 --> 00:24:26.149
Yeah. don't go anywhere.

515
00:24:26.217 --> 00:24:27.817
