527
00:25:07.125 --> 00:25:08.424
That's great. sir.

528
00:25:14.299 --> 00:25:15.665
Sergeant Alvarez.

529
00:25:19.237 --> 00:25:21.504
You know. my great-grandparents.

530
00:25:21.573 --> 00:25:23.573
